deo","display_priority":6}],"free":[{"logo_path":"/vLZKlXUNDcZR7ilvfY9Wr9k80FZ.jpg","provider_id":538,"provider_name":"Plex","display_priority":126},{"logo_path":"/27WMfRN7pQE3j5Khm8fPM7vYyLV.jpg","provider_id":2077,"provider_name":"Plex Channel","display_priority":127},{"logo_path":"/pSUa7lMYLoQAU00ikXoHxmOfTZ9.jpg","provider_id":2409,"provider_name":"Fawesome","display_priority":145}],"link":"https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/364324/watch?locale=US","rent":[{"logo_path":"/qR6FKvnPBx2O37FDg8PNM7efwF3.jpg","provider_id":10,"provider_name":"Amazon Video","display_priority":6}],"flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/pvske1MyAoymrs5bguRfVqYiM9a.jpg","provider_id":9,"provider_name":"Amazon Prime Video","display_priority":5},{"logo_path":"/pPoqVHcko7XoCRrPus4boDW90uM.jpg","provider_id":503,"provider_name":"Hi-YAH","display_priority":122},{"logo_path":"/8aBqoNeGGr0oSA85iopgNZUOTOc.jpg","provider_id":2100,"provider_name":"Amazon Prime Video with Ads","display_priority":204},{"logo_path":"/aysFX0644QGN9wQghp46qn08N0d.jpg","provider_id":2403,"provider_name":"Hi-YAH Amazon Channel","display_priority":259}]},"VA":{"link":"https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/364324/watch?locale=VA","flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/pvske1MyAoymrs5bguRfVqYiM9a.jpg","provider_id":119,"provider_name":"Amazon Prime Video","display_priority":0}]}}},"wikidata_id":"Q20062399","tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-21T21:51:46.863493+00:00","region":null,"main_poster":null,"images":null,"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T07:53:55.637+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"九层妖塔","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1979年，昆仑山发生神秘生物骸骨，由胡八一（赵又廷 饰）率领的探险队深入昆仑山腹地，寻找有关古生物遗迹的更多秘密，却不料在这个过程中遭到不同神秘生物的轮番攻击，并意外坠入九层妖塔，除胡八一外，一行人生死成谜。  　　胡八一退伍后回到北京，重逢了发小王凯旋（冯粒 饰），并在神秘人（李晨 饰）与科考队（凤小岳、唐嫣、李光洁 饰）两股力量的夹缝中重新踏上了探寻未知文明的征程，途中与Shirley杨（姚晨 饰）邂逅，熟识的面孔唤醒了他身处探险队那段日子的记忆。此行凶险，在还没来得及搞清楚Shirley的真实身份之际，胡八一、Shirley、王胖子率领一行人便在王子墓、石油小镇等地遭到不明生物的轰炸，这里所发生的一切再度指向九层妖塔，而这次等待他们的，将是一个尘封已千年的未解之谜……"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Chronicles of the Ghostly Tribe","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In 1979, a young soldier is working in China's snowcapped mountains when an explosion reveals bizarre fossils hidden deep in the mountain caverns. What they discover next will change his life and human history forever."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"구층요탑: 전설의 부활","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1974년 쿤룬산 괴생물체 흔적 발견되고 상하이 고생물 연구소 양쟈린 교수와 749국 대원들은 대규모 탐사에 한창이다. 그러던 어느날 갑작스런 폭발로 생겨난 산 안쪽으로 이어지는 통로를 조사하기 위해 양쟈린 교수, 그의 딸 양핑, 후바이, 중대장 등으로 구성된 탐사대가 길을 떠난다. 본격적인 추적을 시작하려던 찰나 불박쥐의 공격에 탐사대원들 속수무책으로 죽임을 당하게 되고, 가까스로 목숨을 구한 양쟈린 교수는 마침내 '구층요탑'을 발견한다.  만여년전 지구상에 존재했던 외계 종족인 '귀족'이 남긴 유적이자 그들의 저주를 풀 수 있다는 전설로 내려온 '구층요탑'을 후바이와 양핑을 통해 열려던 양쟈린 교수의 계략을 눈치챈 중대장의 방해로 실패로 돌아간다. 설상가상 '구층요탑'의 기관을 잘못 건드리는 바람에 흩어져있던 '귀족'의 괴물이 깨어나 인류를 향한 무차별 공격을 시작되는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"I cacciatori di tesori - Cronache della tribù fantasma","runtime":118,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nel 1979, sulle montagne di Kunlun, viene scoperta una caverna contenente gli scheletri di mostruose creature. Un gruppo di soldati viene mandato in esplorazione e rinviene alcune di queste antiche creature ancora conservate nel ghiaccio, ma dietro la scoperta si nasconde qualcosa di ancor più incredibile: quello che sembrava un tempio sembra in realtà opera di una civiltà aliena."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Crónicas de la Tribu Fantasma","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En 1979, un joven soldado está trabajando en las montañas nevadas de China cuando una explosión revela fósiles extraños ocultos en las profundas cavernas de las montañas. Lo que descubren cambiará su vida y la historia de la humanidad para siempre."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Chronicles of the Ghostly Tribe","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Το 1979 ο Στρατός που εργάζεται στης χιονισμένες βουνοκορφές της Κίνας, αποκαλύπτουν παράξενα απολιθώματα. Μετά από μια έκρηξη ο επικεφαλής τους Στράτου ζητάει εθελοντές για την εξερεύνηση του σπηλαίου. Και η περιπέτεια τους ξεκινάει με τραγικές συνέπειες..."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"Die Chroniken des Geistertempels","runtime":118,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Im Jahre 1979 wird in den Bergen Chinas an der Grenze zur Mongolei ein Sensationsfund entdeckt: Neben gigantischen Fossilien bisher nicht bekannter Kreaturen findet man auch perfekt erhaltene Überreste einer unbekannten Rasse von Menschen. Eine Gruppe von Forschern und Soldaten soll sich das Ganze einmal genauer ansehen und das Geheimnis dahinter lüften. Aber die Expedition tut sich mit dem Finden von Antworten etwas schwer und bringt zunächst etwas noch Seltsameres ans Tageslicht: Bei der Untersuchung stoßen die Wissenschaftler nämlich auf einen mysteriösen Tempel, dessen Existenz noch mehr Fragen aufwirft. Als aus diesem antiken Gemäuer plötzlich gefährliche Geschöpfe in die Welt gelangen, kommen die Forscher langsam einem uralten Geheimnis auf die Schliche: Der Fund könnte die menschliche Evolution für immer verändern."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Chroniques du Royaume des Esprits","runtime":115,"tagline":"Chronique de la Tribu Fantôme","homepage":"","overview":"En 1979, un jeune soldat travaille sur une montagne enneigée quand une explosion révèle des fossiles cachés dans les profondeurs des cavernes de la montagne. Cette découverte va changer sa vie, ainsi que toute l'histoire de l'humanité."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Kroniki Plemienia Duchów","runtime":0,"tagline":"Kroniki Plemienia Duchów","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"ドラゴン・クロニクル 妖魔塔の伝説","runtime":119,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"崑崙山の洞窟で巨大な未確認生物の骨が発見され、調査隊が派遣される。だが、隊は謎の怪物に襲われ壊滅、わずかに生き残ったフー・バーイーと恋人ヤン・ピンらは洞窟の奥にそびえ立つ“妖魔塔”に遭遇する。しかし彼らはそこでも怪物に襲われ、生還したのはバーイーただひとりだった。妖魔塔の研究を始めた彼は、やがて1万年ほど前に塔に封印された異星人が復活をたくらんでいることを知り、新たな調査隊に加わる。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"鬼吹燈之九層妖塔","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1979年，崑崙山發生神秘生物骸骨，由胡八一（趙又廷飾）率領的探險隊深入崑崙山腹地，尋找有關古生物遺蹟的更多秘密，卻不料在這個過程中遭到不同神秘生物的輪番攻擊，並意外墜入九層妖塔，除胡八一外，一行人生死成謎。胡八一退伍後回到北京，重逢了發小王凱旋（馮粒飾），並在神秘人飾）與科考隊（鳳小岳，唐嫣，李光潔飾）兩股力量的夾縫中重新踏上了探尋未知文明的征程，途中與Shirley楊（姚晨飾）邂逅，熟識的面孔喚醒了他身體處探險隊那段日子的記憶。此行凶險，在還沒來得及搞清楚雪莉的真實身份之際，胡八一，雪莉，王胖子率領一行人便在王子墓，石油小鎮等地遭到不明生物的轟炸，這裡所發生的一切再度指向九層妖塔，而這次等待他們的，將是一個塵封已千年的未解之謎......"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Crônicas da Tribo Fantasma","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Em 1979, um jovem soldado está trabalhando nas montanhas cobertas pela neve na China, quando uma explosão revela bizarros fósseis escondidos nas profundezas de uma caverna. A sua descoberta não só irá mudar sua vida para sempre, mas também a história da humanidade.\r Adaptação do livro 'Ghost Blows Out the Light', de Zhang Muye."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Хроники призрачного племени","runtime":118,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"В 1979 году в одной из пещер горной цепи Куньлунь были найдены кости таинственного существа. Ху Байи участвует в экспедиции в глубины этих гор, чтобы отыскать ещё больше скрытых палеонтологических реликвий. Спустившись вниз, исследователи обнаруживают загадочный город, скрытый под толщей горных пород. Город некогда принадлежал могучей цивилизации, которая обладала великой силой и знала тайны жизни и смерти. Радость столь дивной находки омрачили ужасающие существа, напавшие на группу исследователей."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Crônicas da Tribo Fantasma","runtime":0,"tagline":"Crônicas da Tribo Fantasma","homepage":"","overview":"Em 1979, um jovem soldado trabalha nas montanhas cobertas de neve da China quando uma explosão revela fósseis bizarros escondidos nas profundezas das cavernas das montanhas. O que eles descobrirem a seguir mudará sua vida e história humana para sempre."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"鬼吹燈之九層妖塔","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1979 年，崑崙山發生神秘生物骸骨，由胡八一（趙又廷飾）率領的探險隊深入崑崙山腹地，尋找有關古生物遺蹟的更多秘密，卻不料在這個過程中遭到不同神秘生物的輪番攻擊，並意外墜入九層妖塔，除胡八一外，一行人生死成謎。胡八一退伍後回到北京，重逢了發小王凱旋（馮粒飾），並在神秘人飾）與科考隊（鳳小嶽，唐嫣，李光潔飾）兩股力量的夾縫中重新踏上了探尋未知文明的征程，途中與 Shirley 楊（姚晨飾）邂逅，熟識的面孔喚醒了他身體處探險隊那段日子的記憶。此行兇險，在還沒來得及搞清楚雪莉的真實身份之際，胡八一，雪莉，王胖子率領一行人便在王子墓，石油小鎮等地遭到不明生物的轟炸，這裏所發生的一切再度指向九層妖塔，而這次等待他們的，將是一個塵封已千年的未解之謎. . . . . ."},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Chronicles of the Ghostly Tribe","runtime":118,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"V roce 1979 pracuje mladý voják v zasněžených čínských horách, když výbuch odhalí bizarní zkameněliny ukryté hluboko v horských jeskyních. To, co  vzápětí objeví, navždy změní jeho život i historii lidstva."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"อสูรยักษ์แห่งหุบเขามรณะ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ภาพยนตร์จีนแนวแอ็คชันผจญภัย ที่ได้ดัดแปลงมาจากนิยายเรื่องดัง Ghost Blows Out the Light ที่มีคนอ่านอย่างเหนียวแน่น โดยได้ผู้กำกับฝีมือดี ลู่ชวน มากำกับภาพยนตร์เรื่องนี้ ซึ่งผู้กำกับคนดังยังทุ่มเทกับสเปเชียลเอฟเฟกต์จนทำให้ไม่อยากเชื่อว่านี่คือภาพยนตร์จีน นำแสดงโดย เจ้า โย่วถิง ร่วมด้วย เหยา เฉิน, ไรเดียน แวน-ฮานน์, หลี่เฉิน และ ถัง เยียน กับเรื่องราวของ สองหนุ่มสาวที่ได้ออกมาผจญภัยการขุดถ้ำลึกลับที่ซ่อนตัวอยู่ในเทือกเขาที่ปกคลุมไปด้วยหิมะ ซึ่งภายในถ้ำได้มีการค้นพบซากดึกดำบรรพ์ของสัตว์ประหลาดขนาดใหญ่ที่มีลักษณะคล้ายมังกรและฝูงสัตว์เล็กๆ สีน้ำเงินคล้ายค้างคาวที่เผาทำลายทุกคนที่ไปแตะมัน เขาและเธอยังได้ค้นพบความลับบางอย่างของมนุษย์และภูติผี"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"მოჩვენებების ტომის ქრონიკები","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1979 წელს კუნლუნის მთიანეთის გამოქვაბულში იპოვეს იდუმალი არსების ძვლები. ჰუ ბაიი (მარკ ჩაო) ხელმძღვანელობს ექსპედიციას ამ მთების სიღრმეში, რათა აღმოაჩინოს მეტი ფარული პალეონტოლოგიური რელიქვიები. ქვევით ჩასვლისას მკვლევარები აღმოაჩენენ იდუმალ ქალაქს, რომელიც იმალება კლდეების ფენის ქვეშ. ქალაქი ოდესღაც ეკუთვნოდა უძლიერეს ცივილიზაციას, რომელსაც გააჩნდა დიდი ძალა და იცოდა სიცოცხლისა და სიკვდილის საიდუმლოებები. ასეთი საოცარი აღმოჩენის სიხარულს დაჩრდილა საშინელი არსებები, რომლებიც თავს დაესხნენ მკვლევართა ჯგუფს."},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"},{"data":{"title":"Ma Thổi Đèn: Chín Tầng Tháp Quỷ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Năm 1979, trên núi Côn Luân phát hiện hài cốt sinh vật thần bí, Hồ Bát Nhất cùng đoàn thám hiểm tìm kiếm bí mật của di tích cổ trên đó đến được Cửu Tầng Yêu tháp. Nhiều người trong đoàn bỏ mạng trên đường đi hoặc mất tích, không rõ sống chết.Hồ Bát Nhất sau khi giải ngũ trở lại Bắc Kinh, gặp lại bạn thân Vương Khải Tuyền, một lần nữa bước lên hành trình tìm kiếm nền văn minh cổ. Trên đường cùng Shirley Dương tình cờ gặp gỡ, khuôn mặt quen thuộc của cô làm anh nhớ lại những ngày tháng ở cùng đoàn thám hiểm kia. Chuyến đi nguy hiểm, cả đoàn đã bị quái vật tấn công, để rồi nhận ra chuyện phát sinh nơi này lại một lần nữa liên quan đến Cửu Tầng Yêu tháp, mà lần này chờ đợi bọn họ, chính là một bí ẩn chưa có lời đáp đã phủ bụi cả ngàn năm…"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In 1979 werkt een jonge soldaat in de met sneeuw bedekte bergen van China wanneer een explosie bizarre fossielen onthult die diep in de berggrotten verborgen zijn. Wat ze vervolgens ontdekken, zal zijn leven en menselijke geschiedenis voor altijd veranderen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Хроники на призрачния народ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"През 1979 г. млад войник работи в покрити със сняг планини на Китай, когато експлозия разкрива странни вкаменелости, скрити дълбоко в планинските пещери. Това, което откриват след това, ще промени живота и човешката история завинаги."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":299824,"adult":false,"title":"Mojin: The Lost Legend","video":false,"overview":"Three tomb raiders retire from their roles and move to New York to enjoy the rest of their lives. However, they are asked to resume duty in order to find out the reason behind the loss of a loved one.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4717,"vote_count":257,"poster_path":"/supoIHkh3dzDi1XmvK8tgGlkGNS.jpg","release_date":"2015-12-18","vote_average":6.247,"backdrop_path":"/6ilMT6VCADu5F1Xr9LjiVxQSXPp.jpg","original_title":"寻龙诀","original_language":"zh"},{"id":52324,"adult":false,"title":"Sixty Million Dollar Man","video":false,"overview":"A rich playboy gets blown up by a gangster when he flirts with the gangster's wife. Through a series of circumstances, his professor makes him a synthetic body that allows him to change into anything he wants.","genre_ids":[35,14,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1689,"vote_count":90,"poster_path":"/xhTTKU7SfZQ3pg3gmelSGJQqZdF.jpg","release_date":"1995-08-19","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/pkFlSypkCFKaFdiA9omyplXaIE6.jpg","original_title":"百變星君","original_language":"cn"},{"id":479469,"adult":false,"title":"Adam: The Mirror","video":false,"overview":"Oats Studios brings to life the next chapter in the Adam story, made in real-time using Unity. Join our amnesiac hero as he discovers a clue about what and who he is.","genre_ids":[878,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2428,"vote_count":50,"poster_path":"/3GdDzzcZp4Fd0FrySZL5CApoCJT.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-03","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/3D0lQ8X3y7n0OatJK0l6NZM88Xo.jpg","original_title":"Adam: The Mirror","original_language":"en"},{"id":411442,"adult":false,"title":"Time Raiders","video":false,"overview":"Time Raiders is based on the online novel series Daomu Biji written by Xu Lei.  It tells the story of explorers searching for the secrets of immortality in ancient tombs","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8082,"vote_count":27,"poster_path":"/qtbJL3pWPJIO8KGqZpRLEn4jmQp.jpg","release_date":"2016-08-18","vote_average":5.296,"backdrop_path":"/96SopW64ZEipVXtPzHb3pOERtWu.jpg","original_title":"盗墓笔记","original_language":"zh"},{"id":962486,"adult":false,"title":"Desert Shadows","video":false,"overview":"After the death of their father, two brothers decide to travel to hunt and strengthen their bonds. However, they are surprised when they themselves see the prey of a deadly creature that roams the desert.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.49,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/s93lFCuJsHcum2h4TJaE42kgei1.jpg","release_date":"2022-04-23","vote_average":3.321,"backdrop_path":"/aYMq6Qfd4LOHU0VRWwL9wWz637P.jpg","original_title":"Desert Shadows","original_language":"en"},{"id":364391,"adult":false,"title":"Time to Love","video":false,"overview":"A single modern-day city girl name Zhang Xiaowen accidentally travels back in time to the Qing Dynasty and becomes Ruoxi, but gets caught up in a web of love and politics in the royal court of Emperor Kangxi.","genre_ids":[14,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5681,"vote_count":6,"poster_path":"/3swoyMgMPog2ZgdRdwtBSuyYfdo.jpg","release_date":"2015-08-07","vote_average":5.083,"backdrop_path":"/qec7JUAYMBSnDcZKZcIOFxNC6UP.jpg","original_title":"新步步惊心","original_language":"zh"},{"id":571446,"adult":false,"title":"Mojin: The Worm Valley","video":false,"overview":"Legendary tomb explorer Hu Bayi is on a dangerous mission as he seeks out the Tomb of Emperor Xian, located on an island of monstrous creatures in this mystical action-adventure.","genre_ids":[28,14,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.06,"vote_count":58,"poster_path":"/Acwua30iAaIiNTBac68iVZTyYrH.jpg","release_date":"2018-12-29","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/8NLs4rogROu2eNPxdTUqExiLak2.jpg","original_title":"云南虫谷","original_language":"zh"},{"id":31850,"adult":false,"title":"Breathless","video":false,"overview":"Sang-hoon is a lowlife gangster, a debt collector exercising thuggish ways to collect his money. The recipient of nothing but anger since his childhood, he expresses himself through violence. When he finally encounters someone who can stand up to him, feisty school-girl Yoon-hee they become unlikely friends.","genre_ids":[80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0608,"vote_count":134,"poster_path":"/9ZPPjSoPWN4BPea2h8sd6L7skSI.jpg","release_date":"2009-04-16","vote_average":7.112,"backdrop_path":"/nMxucwkm4dAT7kfxV98dXqs6P0w.jpg","original_title":"똥파리","original_language":"ko"},{"id":11331,"adult":false,"title":"The Old Man and the Sea","video":false,"overview":"Santiago is an aging, down-on-his-luck, Cuban fisherman who, after catching nothing for nearly 3 months, hooks a huge Marlin and struggles to land it far out in the Gulf Stream.","genre_ids":[12,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8349,"vote_count":160,"poster_path":"/6Q34dJL6m1vdzAr0jDDKDmNL52e.jpg","release_date":"1958-10-07","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/5S916KQ6Wmn0pDFoeknIvpMgL9v.jpg","original_title":"The Old Man and the Sea","original_language":"en"},{"id":40069,"adult":false,"title":"Premonition","video":false,"overview":"While stopped at a roadside phone booth for transmitting his work through the Internet to the university, Professor Hideki Satomi finds a scrap of newspaper with the picture of his five-year-old daughter Nana in the obituary section.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2468,"vote_count":130,"poster_path":"/Aarfof4kkVvxw9aKETcOGX8vFaZ.jpg","release_date":"2004-10-02","vote_average":6.323,"backdrop_path":"/wwjBU3s8oJtAs0qHKEcw2mDyRqY.jpg","original_title":"予言","original_language":"ja"},{"id":20424,"adult":false,"title":"Invaders from Mars","video":false,"overview":"A boy tries to stop aliens that have taken over his town and are brainwashing its inhabitants.","genre_ids":[878,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6056,"vote_count":199,"poster_path":"/hoHCZJWrHwEXfog7ql0DtGbzmv4.jpg","release_date":"1953-04-09","vote_average":5.915,"backdrop_path":"/f26rSgpMWGNOtW4pdIpUDQSnbj3.jpg","original_title":"Invaders from Mars","original_language":"en"},{"id":506763,"adult":false,"title":"Detective Dee: The Four Heavenly Kings","video":false,"overview":"Dee, the detective serving Chinese empress Wu Zetian, is called upon to investigate a series of strange events in Loyang, including the appearance of mysterious warriors wearing Chiyou ghost masks, foxes that speak human language and the pillar sculptures in the palace coming alive.","genre_ids":[28,14,12,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.4288,"vote_count":210,"poster_path":"/nZ3XTA5ZlGOj92jRBSYglW8r9QY.jpg","release_date":"2018-07-27","vote_average":6.281,"backdrop_path":"/rzGHVq2BCMwjp93QaKYoLPSaSrp.jpg","original_title":"狄仁杰之四大天王","original_language":"zh"},{"id":17186,"adult":false,"title":"Supercross","video":false,"overview":"Faced with the suspicious death of their father, two brothers must motivate one another to get back on their bikes and take the Las Vegas Motocross Championships by storm.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.6466,"vote_count":144,"poster_path":"/82dbqeFOA2iPhwWuciZItw1ELew.jpg","release_date":"2005-08-16","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/oC3ya5pKxKy8BXjj3eXDit7iz3e.jpg","original_title":"Supercross","original_language":"en"},{"id":372439,"adult":false,"title":"Picardía mexicana","video":false,"overview":"An academic tags along among a crew of rowdy delivery-truck drivers, taking notes on their colorful and idiomatic use of language.","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.9451,"vote_count":70,"poster_path":"/fNguKu5kiqF41DVL5syOwJ0K6Tk.jpg","release_date":"1978-12-21","vote_average":7.257,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Picardía mexicana","original_language":"es"},{"id":797946,"adult":false,"title":"The Djinn","video":false,"overview":"A mute boy is trapped in his apartment with a sinister monster when he makes a wish to fulfill his heart’s greatest desire.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4534,"vote_count":183,"poster_path":"/yk0XkUc3kz6Mrnk9y7o7weSOpO0.jpg","release_date":"2021-05-14","vote_average":5.675,"backdrop_path":"/kryYpNFiYyPUVC7SXrHk2pjRj4y.jpg","original_title":"The Djinn","original_language":"en"},{"id":676685,"adult":false,"title":"Panda Bear in Africa","video":false,"overview":"A young adventurous panda travels from China to Africa to rescue his best friend, Jielong the Dragon, who has been kidnapped. On his journey, he discovers a strange amazing new world of mountains, deserts and jungles.","genre_ids":[16,12,35,10751],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.9233,"vote_count":76,"poster_path":"/wxpu7svVqA0ALYpofQBPujGelN3.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-15","vote_average":7.072,"backdrop_path":"/youmOAJwM4XCoHAgeYNXACA7Buc.jpg","original_title":"Pandabeer in Afrika","original_language":"nl"},{"id":1137205,"adult":false,"title":"Last Straw","video":false,"overview":"A rural roadside diner becomes the host of a maniacal killing spree – leaving a young waitress to clean up the mess. After hard-headed Nancy fires the staff at her dad’s diner, she decides to cover the last shift of the night by herself. Little does she know, she is far from alone. The day is coming back to haunt her and when things begin to spiral out of control, she must fight for her life over the course of one long night.","genre_ids":[27,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.6208,"vote_count":123,"poster_path":"/hgpUvybRQzRK6UagoHNQRrO8sUg.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-20","vote_average":6.13,"backdrop_path":"/A6KaZEXI9NJ1nwjmzTQDkiDTDWN.jpg","original_title":"Last Straw","original_language":"en"},{"id":614427,"adult":false,"title":"Three Perfect Daughters","video":false,"overview":"Three families go into crisis when their daughters get engaged because they are convinced that their young daughters have all chosen a wrong partner.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3081,"vote_count":280,"poster_path":"/7M9MRi2N5Pen1C7HX7Ii5l57bja.jpg","release_date":"2020-07-02","vote_average":5.939,"backdrop_path":"/cd6I4X5SY8qdpr8Mb932MJz4tez.jpg","original_title":"È per il tuo bene","original_language":"it"},{"id":359364,"adult":false,"title":"Human","video":false,"overview":"A collection of stories about and images of our world, offering an immersion to the core of what it means to be human. Through these stories full of love and happiness, as well as hatred and violence, it brings us face to face with the Other, making us reflect on our lives. From stories of everyday experiences to accounts of the most unbelievable lives, these poignant encounters share a rare sincerity and underline who we are – our darker side, but also what is most noble in us, and what is universal. Our Earth is shown at its most sublime through never-before-seen aerial images accompanied by soaring music, resulting in an ode to the beauty of the world, providing a moment to draw breath and for introspection. This film is a politically engaged work which allows us to embrace the human condition and to reflect on the meaning of our existence.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1082,"vote_count":303,"poster_path":"/l02W63OGQKYugJrs3Uw8nA9gii4.jpg","release_date":"2015-09-12","vote_average":8.5,"backdrop_path":"/c0gtBfDyOrba9e5wnFjrxn8rxQr.jpg","original_title":"Human","original_language":"fr"},{"id":513692,"adult":false,"title":"Raging Fire","video":false,"overview":"Cheung Sung-bong is a highly respected cop with a long history of success in dangerous cases. However, his past soon comes back to haunt him when a former protégé resurfaces, seeking revenge.","genre_ids":[28,80,53,12,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.142,"vote_count":284,"poster_path":"/flFQEHlW4omcU47jwgNKPw7SpF3.jpg","release_date":"2021-07-28","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/qLtREPyJgxewgK3l68epEQeHTVR.jpg","original_title":"怒火","original_language":"cn"}],"similar_content":[{"id":283034,"adult":false,"title":"Neonnächte - Der U-Bahn-Schlitzer","video":false,"overview":"A new case for the energetic criminal investigation officer Beate Stein: The half-undressed corpse of a subway driver is found in a subway tunnel. It soon seems as if the perpetrator has been found in a convicted female murderer. But after his death, the murders continue ...","genre_ids":[80,53,10770],"popularity":0.186,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2000-01-05","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Neonnächte - Der U-Bahn-Schlitzer","original_language":"de"},{"id":869768,"adult":false,"title":"Naked Angel : The Red Room","video":false,"overview":"Matsunaga, the president of a real estate company, spends his week in a secret hideaway to forget his title and social status. One day, he meets Fumiko, a girl who has a mysterious charm, and is gradually attracted to him. Matsunaga deepened his relationship with her, but suddenly a mysterious man appeared.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":0.549,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/cUogOofe4BEOaNCWqWshBS8ME7V.jpg","release_date":"2021-04-02","vote_average":1,"backdrop_path":"/oEjgBLnrhVjwZMzTTBIuLyHfdlM.jpg","original_title":"裸の天使 赤い部屋","original_language":"ja"},{"id":476907,"adult":false,"title":"Pretty Poison","video":false,"overview":"A clueless cheerleader falls for a mysterious young man who tells her he's a secret agent. But the truth is much simpler and darker.","genre_ids":[53,10749,10770],"popularity":2.5324,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/wOXwoTPRs6HU7h5ptfIrsrW2z9C.jpg","release_date":"1996-09-24","vote_average":2.5,"backdrop_path":"/cJQb6ii1fJcKpVjq6d1GjhOFnvR.jpg","original_title":"Pretty Poison","original_language":"en"},{"id":12764,"adult":false,"title":"Missing in Action 2: The Beginning","video":true,"overview":"Prequel to the first Missing In Action, set in the early 1980s it shows the capture of Colonel Braddock during the Vietnam war in the 1970s, and his captivity with other American POWs in a brutal prison camp, and his plans to escape.","genre_ids":[28,10752],"popularity":1.0345,"vote_count":309,"poster_path":"/vOgiL2KQYyTHJ225lT5QB5B9kO0.jpg","release_date":"1985-03-01","vote_average":5.735,"backdrop_path":"/7xADC2HSQw9fAQuPMPsZS2XVPV7.jpg","original_title":"Missing in Action 2: The Beginning","original_language":"en"},{"id":12775,"adult":false,"title":"Flesh + Blood","video":false,"overview":"A band of medieval mercenaries take revenge on a noble Lord who stiffs them by kidnapping the betrothed of the noble's son. As the plague and warfare cut a swathe of destruction throughout the land, the mercenaries hole up in a castle and await their fate.","genre_ids":[12,18],"popularity":2.0355,"vote_count":423,"poster_path":"/bjUYC4uC82oASTMPkb6iGCYOO2e.jpg","release_date":"1985-08-30","vote_average":6.564,"backdrop_path":"/1bkt7iYDDLHsPCINaplT3rQ116N.jpg","original_title":"Flesh + Blood","original_language":"en"},{"id":12535,"adult":false,"title":"High Anxiety","video":false,"overview":"A psychiatrist with intense acrophobia (fear of heights) goes to work for a mental institution run by doctors who appear to be crazier than their patients, and have secrets that they are willing to commit murder to keep.","genre_ids":[35,9648,53],"popularity":1.3194,"vote_count":388,"poster_path":"/hCazLbbAveK7Ohc2xT3b3GioNjR.jpg","release_date":"1977-12-25","vote_average":6.448,"backdrop_path":"/uZK6kGcO2RRteHoEgkpH4Mwa3lf.jpg","original_title":"High Anxiety","original_language":"en"},{"id":12633,"adult":false,"title":"The Star Chamber","video":false,"overview":"As violence escalates in Los Angeles and heinous murders are committed, Steven Hardin, a young judge of the California Supreme Court, must struggle with his tortured conscience and growing despair as he watches helplessly as the ruthless criminals brought before his court go free because clever lawyers find obscure loopholes in the law.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":0.8283,"vote_count":178,"poster_path":"/uXtsxFFWQmoUQu4qbBdOprEpv2Y.jpg","release_date":"1983-08-05","vote_average":6.017,"backdrop_path":"/f8O32f2JOnDXwiVOl2IUsXZ5ABt.jpg","original_title":"The Star Chamber","original_language":"en"},{"id":12651,"adult":false,"title":"Memphis Belle","video":false,"overview":"The \"Memphis Belle\" is a World War II bomber, piloted by a young crew on dangerous bombing raids into Europe. The crew only have to make one more bombing raid before they have finished their duty and can go home. In the briefing before their last flight, the crew discover that the target for the day is Bremen.","genre_ids":[18,10752,28],"popularity":1.3035,"vote_count":409,"poster_path":"/epsraI4swsSu9Fyefj7vPPhsOHK.jpg","release_date":"1990-09-07","vote_average":6.732,"backdrop_path":"/8kVhN0OC5AmdHJJ1BxKCakZhvQO.jpg","original_title":"Memphis Belle","original_language":"en"},{"id":12684,"adult":false,"title":"Sabotage","video":false,"overview":"Karl Anton Verloc and his wife own a small cinema in a quiet London suburb where they live seemingly happily. But Mrs. Verloc does not know that her husband has a secret that will affect their relationship and threaten her teenage brother's life.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"popularity":0.7912,"vote_count":357,"poster_path":"/A6cyOt9mhmvWA2uHcVsGkcCaHCz.jpg","release_date":"1937-01-08","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/lZL7Z8102qbLJqtlC2cJutq0FQ7.jpg","original_title":"Sabotage","original_language":"en"},{"id":476669,"adult":false,"title":"The King's Man","video":false,"overview":"As a collection of history's worst tyrants and criminal masterminds gather to plot a war to wipe out millions, one man must race against time to stop them.","genre_ids":[28,12,53],"popularity":6.5724,"vote_count":4957,"poster_path":"/iMjSfMUuCkCE7z5fzGtjeDusPD3.jpg","release_date":"2021-12-22","vote_average":6.721,"backdrop_path":"/oQPbZ5e6J9fuAyv4Gl0mMZMIyPI.jpg","original_title":"The King's Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":12576,"adult":false,"title":"Deathwatch","video":false,"overview":"In the brutal trench fighting of the First World War, a British Infantry Company is separated from their regiment after a fierce battle. Attempting to return to their lines, the British soldiers discover what appears to be a bombed out German trench, abandoned except for a few dazed German soldiers. After killing most of the Germans, and taking one prisoner, the British company fortifies to hold the trench until reinforcements can arrive. Soon, however, strange things being to happen as a sense of evil descends on the trench and the British begin turn on each other.","genre_ids":[18,27,53,10752],"popularity":3.1815,"vote_count":221,"poster_path":"/R8qod2CvMi5iH2gfr043dMSM1y.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-06","vote_average":5.747,"backdrop_path":"/kscbTFqCnRm43yDQVzAVL7N3CUa.jpg","original_title":"Deathwatch","original_language":"en"},{"id":12607,"adult":false,"title":"Kamikaze '89","video":false,"overview":"In a futuristic, totalitarian society wherein the government controls all facets of the media, a homicide detective investigates a string of bombings and uncovers more than he bargained for.","genre_ids":[878,53],"popularity":0.3843,"vote_count":25,"poster_path":"/4kaOGOc17LoszAlsj2WKFgapBY8.jpg","release_date":"1982-07-16","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/lF5b0rZzcmY546uBQU8cEEVA91B.jpg","original_title":"Kamikaze 1989","original_language":"de"},{"id":12611,"adult":false,"title":"The Fury","video":false,"overview":"When a devious plot separates CIA agent Peter Sandza from his son, Robin, the distraught father manages to see through the ruse. Taken because of his psychic abilities, Robin is being held by Ben Childress, who is studying people with supernatural powers in hopes of developing their talents as weapons. Soon Peter pairs up with Gillian, a teen who has telekinesis, to find and rescue Robin.","genre_ids":[27,878,53],"popularity":1.3255,"vote_count":392,"poster_path":"/tkIXykrfndqf11Lb7U5RbIRa13b.jpg","release_date":"1978-03-10","vote_average":6.297,"backdrop_path":"/bgTgA6ZckxKMy0oQyEFenxmxdGK.jpg","original_title":"The Fury","original_language":"en"},{"id":282800,"adult":false,"title":"Raining Blood","video":false,"overview":"One day, Naoto receives a package. Inside he finds a book, ‘LIVE’. At the same time, he receives an image on mobile phone of his mother being kidnapped and a call from a mysterious man. “If you don’ t want us to inject the killer virus in your mother, find the hints hidden in the novel and head for the goal in the death race!” Naoto starts running to save his mother with the book in his hand.","genre_ids":[53,35,27],"popularity":0.5878,"vote_count":12,"poster_path":"/qz4HgerNnLPsKoBEgqWNbUVwCjr.jpg","release_date":"2014-05-10","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/l5TnejmsA9aeR0pdHPZwqXzOlpV.jpg","original_title":"ライヴ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":283281,"adult":false,"title":"The Scapegoat","video":false,"overview":"Il Fornaretto di Venezia (US TV title: The Scapegoat) is a 1963 Italian film directed by Duccio Tessari who co-wrote screenplay with Marcello Fondato, based on novel by Francesco Dall'Ongaro.  It tells the story of 16th century's Venice where a young worker is sentenced to death on the suspicion of attacking a noble.","genre_ids":[36,12],"popularity":0.3535,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/d80eYjcsSCn4nHOmzLBPf5MFi4P.jpg","release_date":"1963-08-23","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/lUZlNcvLw4Z1nWJzNPrxt4TV7xY.jpg","original_title":"Il fornaretto di Venezia","original_language":"it"},{"id":476927,"adult":false,"title":"Travis McGee","video":false,"overview":"Travis McGee is a world-weary private eye trying to help boat skipper friend Van Harder salvage his reputation that sank when his boat ran aground, resulting in a death that might have been faked.","genre_ids":[28,18,9648,10770],"popularity":0.3895,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/8W1yexF9hHZRh3DpIpvvZfm1NFG.jpg","release_date":"1983-05-18","vote_average":4.5,"backdrop_path":"/g2ktIlFwousoNMRQhjEgm7LsVlo.jpg","original_title":"Travis McGee","original_language":"en"},{"id":869886,"adult":false,"title":"A Man","video":false,"overview":"Akira works as a lawyer. One day, he meets with his former client Rie, who asks Akira to perform a background check on her late husband Daisuke.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"popularity":1.0341,"vote_count":75,"poster_path":"/28BHeDbC0307Gzt467XLdVNJuag.jpg","release_date":"2022-11-18","vote_average":7.053,"backdrop_path":"/uQH89ABEDUzgVr06ILurTDO60jw.jpg","original_title":"ある男","original_language":"ja"},{"id":12837,"adult":false,"title":"The Secret Life of Bees","video":false,"overview":"Set in South Carolina in 1964, this is the tale of Lily Owens a 14 year-old girl who is haunted by the memory of her late mother. To escape her lonely life and troubled relationship with her father, Lily flees with Rosaleen, her caregiver and only friend, to a South Carolina town that holds the secret to her mother's past.","genre_ids":[10751,12,18],"popularity":1.3098,"vote_count":562,"poster_path":"/m1LGEeoYfc6crbfG8WmTK